data.value:
SELECT AA.SLIP_CODE SLIP_CODE , AA.SLIP_NAME SLIP_NAME , AA.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE , AA.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMOG_NAME , '' SEQ , AA.HOSP_CODE HOSP_CODE , :f_user MEMB , '' MEMB_GUBUN , NVL(AA.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') WONNAE_DRG_YN , ROWNUM FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT :f_user DOCTOR, B.SLIP_CODE SLIP_CODE, C.SLIP_NAME SLIP_NAME, A.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE, B.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMOG_NAME, '' SEQ, A.HOSP_CODE HOSP_CODE, '' MEMB_GUBUN, NVL(B.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') WONNAE_DRG_YN, COUNT(*) FROM OCS2003 A ,OCS0103 B ,OCS0102 C WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND 'I' = :f_io_gubun AND SUBSTR(A.INPUT_DOCTOR, 3) = :f_user AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = :f_order_gubun -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND :f_order_date BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE AND B.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE '%'||:f_search_word||'%' AND NVL(B.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') LIKE :f_wonnae_drg_yn -- AND C.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.SLIP_CODE = B.SLIP_CODE
GROUP BY :f_user , B.SLIP_CODE , C.SLIP_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME , '' , A.HOSP_CODE , NVL(B.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N')
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT :f_user DOCTOR , B.SLIP_CODE SLIP_CODE , C.SLIP_NAME SLIP_NAME, A.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE, B.HANGMOG_NAME HANGMGO_NAME, '' SEQ , A.HOSP_CODE HOSP_CODE , '' MEMB_GUBUN , NVL(B.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') WONNAE_DRG_YN, COUNT(*) FROM OCS1003 A ,OCS0103 B ,OCS0102 C WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND 'O' = :f_io_gubun AND SUBSTR(A.DOCTOR, 3) = :f_user AND B.ORDER_GUBUN = :f_order_gubun -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND :f_order_date BETWEEN B.START_DATE AND B.END_DATE AND B.HANGMOG_NAME_INX LIKE '%'||:f_search_word||'%' AND NVL(B.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') LIKE :f_wonnae_drg_yn -- AND C.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.SLIP_CODE = B.SLIP_CODE GROUP BY :f_user , B.SLIP_CODE , C.SLIP_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE , B.HANGMOG_NAME , '' , A.HOSP_CODE , NVL(B.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') ORDER BY 10 DESC ) AA WHERE ROWNUM < 50

data.value: SELECT A.SLIP_CODE , B.SLIP_NAME , A.HANGMOG_CODE , A.HANGMOG_NAME , NVL(A.WONNAE_DRG_YN, 'N') WONNAE_DRG_YN FROM OCS0102 B , OCS0103 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND SUBSTR(A.YAK_KIJUN_CODE, 1, :f_filter) = SUBSTR(:f_yak_kijun_code, 1, :f_filter) AND NVL(TO_DATE(:f_order_date, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), TRUNC(SYSDATE)) BETWEEN A.START_DATE AND A.END_DATE AND NVL(A.WONNAE_DRG_YN,'N') = 'Y' AND A.ORDER_GUBUN IN ('C', 'D') AND A.HANGMOG_CODE != :f_hangmog_code -- AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.SLIP_CODE = A.SLIP_CODE ORDER BY 1, 3
